    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the tomatoes have started to break down, add the <strong>vegetable</strong> <strong>stock</strong>, <strong>chopped tomatoes</strong> and <strong>drained black beans</strong> to the pan and cook for 1 min further or until thickened and gently bubbling – these are your <strong>smoky beans</strong></p>",
      "order": 5,
