    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Make 1 well per person in the smoky beans and crack your <strong>eggs </strong>into the wells</p><p>Cover with a lid and cook for 4-6 min or until the eggs are done to your liking – these are your <strong>smoky beans & eggs</strong></p><p>Add your <strong>wholemeal pittas </strong>to the toaster for 1-2 min until warmed through, then slice into triangles – these are your <strong>pitta chips</strong></p>",
