    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, cut your <strong>avocado[s]</strong> in half lengthways, around the stone[s]</p><p>Remove the stone[s] using a spoon, then scoop out the <strong>avocado flesh</strong> and slice finely lengthways</p><p>Roughly chop your<strong> chives</strong></p>",
