    {
      "instruction": "<p>Serve the <strong>smoky beans & eggs </strong>in bowls with the <strong>sliced avocado</strong> and <strong>pitta chips</strong> to the side – this is your <strong>smoky Mexican-style breakfast bowl</strong></p><p>Sprinkle over the <strong>chopped chives </strong>and season with a generous grind of <strong>black pepper</strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
